title: Shinchireem
text:
Shinchireem (Korean: 신치림; Hanja: 信治琳) is a South Korean rock band. Their members consist of Yoon Jong-shin, Jo Jung-chi and Hareem. Shinchireem is currently signed to Mystic Entertainment. Shinchireem released their first single, "Unknown Number" in February 2012.
